title: Surface 11 - Strings of Fate Collector's Edition [ASG]
description:
No Need For Patches Or Serials Just Run Installer And Enjoy The Game!

Elephant Games brings you the latest installment of the Surface series!
Your little sister has been kidnapped by two Brothers of Fate! With the help of a third Brother, it’s up to you to save her. With the odds stacked against you, can you find a way into another world and rescue her in time?! Find out in this spell-binding hidden-object puzzle adventure!

The Collector’s Edition features: 
• Meet and old friend in the bonus game!
• Create the perfect home for Toto using Collectibles
• Replay puzzles and mini-games
• Enjoy concept art, music, wallpapers, and more!
• Consult the helpful Strategy Guide

System Requirements:
OS: Windows XP/Vista/Win7/Win8/Win10
CPU: 2 GHz RAM: 1024 MB
DirectX: 9.0
Hard Drive: 2.72 GB
